{
  "title": "Bônus casado com clube abre janela de emissão",
  "body_content": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\"><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\"><title>The Loyalty — Nº 28</title></head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;background:#F1ECE1;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111\">\n  <span style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0\">A conta fecha para quem já é do clube. Para o resto, é caro.</span>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#F1ECE1\">\n    <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 12px\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#FAF7F0\">\n        <tr><td style=\"border-bottom:4px double #111111;padding:20px 24px\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;color:#111111\">The Loyalty</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:12px;color:#555555\">Nº 28</td>\n          </tr><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:11px;color:#8A8578;padding-top:4px\">QUARTA-FEIRA · 8H00</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:11px;color:#8A8578;padding-top:4px\">LEITURA DE 5 MIN</td>\n          </tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:12px 24px 32px\">\n          <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;padding-top:12px;margin:28px 0 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#555555\">O sinal do dia</div>\n          <div style=\"border-left:3px solid #315CFF;padding-left:20px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#111111\">Dois programas abriram bônus de transferência na mesma semana em que a compra de pontos de origem entrou em promoção. Quando as duas pontas coincidem, a janela é curta e a conta importa mais que a manchete.</div>\n          <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;padding-top:12px;margin:28px 0 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#555555\">Deal Desk</div>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #E5E0D5;border-radius:8px\">\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:20px\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#8A8578\">Transferência bonificada · Esfera → Latam Pass</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;color:#111111;margin-top:8px\">100% de bônus com compra de origem em desconto</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#555555;margin-top:8px\">Origem em promoção e transferência bonificada ativas ao mesmo tempo. VPM estimado de resgate em torno de R$ 33/milheiro dá spread positivo para quem já é do clube. Vigência confirmada até sexta.</div>\n        <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#111111;border-radius:8px;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">custo origem</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">R$ 1.200,00</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">pontos origem</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">50.000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">bônus</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">100%</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">milhas finais</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">100.000</td></tr>\n        <tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-top:1px solid #3D3A34;padding-top:8px\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"color:#00C48C;padding-top:2px\">CPM final</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#00C48C;font-weight:bold\">R$ 12,00 /milheiro</td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#D9F4E9;color:#007A57;border-radius:9999px;padding:4px 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em\">VALE AGIR <span style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:14px\">88</span></span> <span style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#111111\">Vale agir para quem já é do clube e tem emissão planejada.</span></div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555555;margin-top:10px\">Fonte: Regulamento oficial · vigência confirmada 08/07, 6h30</div>\n      </td></tr>\n    </table><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;padding-top:12px;margin:28px 0 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#555555\">Deal Desk</div>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #E5E0D5;border-radius:8px\">\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:20px\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#8A8578\">Compra de pontos · aguardando confirmação</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;color:#111111;margin-top:8px\">Rumor de 120% em compra direta ainda sem regulamento</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#555555;margin-top:8px\">Sinal veio de post social sem página oficial. Sem vigência nem regra publicada, não sustenta recomendação — entra apenas como radar de monitoramento.</div>\n        <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#111111;border-radius:8px;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">preço base</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">R$ 38,00 /mil</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#8A8578;padding:2px 0\">bônus anunciado</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#FAF7F0;padding:2px 0\">120% (não confirmado)</td></tr>\n        <tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-top:1px solid #3D3A34;padding-top:8px\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"color:#00C48C;padding-top:2px\">CPM final</td><td align=\"right\" style=\"color:#00C48C;font-weight:bold\">aguardando confirmação</td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#F1ECE1;color:#555555;border-radius:9999px;padding:4px 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em\">NÃO CONFIRMADO</span> <span style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#111111\">Radar. Não agir sem regulamento oficial.</span></div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555555;margin-top:10px\">Fonte: Post social público, sem página oficial (nível 4)</div>\n      </td></tr>\n    </table>\n          <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;padding-top:12px;margin:28px 0 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#555555\">Fecha logo</div><div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#111111;margin-top:8px\">\n        <span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#F2C94C;color:#111111;border-radius:4px;padding:2px 8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:bold;margin-right:8px\">VENCE EM 72H</span>Compra de pontos Esfera com 30% de desconto encerra sexta. <span style=\"font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;font-size:14px\">CPM R$ 19,80</span> para o público do clube\n      </div>\n          <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;padding-top:12px;margin:28px 0 12px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#555555\">Fontes</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555555;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://www.latampass.latam.com\" style=\"color:#315CFF;text-decoration:underline\">Regulamento oficial Latam Pass (exemplo)</a> · <a href=\"https://www.esfera.com.vc\" style=\"color:#315CFF;text-decoration:underline\">Portal Esfera (exemplo)</a></div>\n          <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #E5E0D5;margin-top:24px;padding-top:16px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#8A8578\">\n            Edição ilustrativa. Números de exemplo. Promoções podem mudar sem aviso. Confira sempre as regras no site oficial antes de comprar, transferir ou resgatar.\n          </div>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</body></html>",
